title: Cowboys-Bears TNF Preview (Football 12/5)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to preview Cowboys-Bears on Thursday Night Football. The guys discuss the pressure Dallas is facing after a Thanksgiving Day loss, how Jason Garrett continues to hold his team back, if Mitchell Trubisky can replicate his effort from last Thursday and the sneaky greatness of Allen Robinson before issuing player props and picks for the game.
